
IRC spamtrap
------------
Spam Trapper.


Requirement
-----------
* IRC Server running with ngircd
* Oper
* NodeJS
* (Lib)SQLite3 


Installation
------------
* Clone this repository
    $ git clone https://github.com/Yonle/irc-spamtrap

* Edit spamtrap.js and follow the instructions on the comments.


SQLite3 Schema
--------------
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS bots (nick TEXT, host TEXT, date INT, UNIQUE(host));


